   <text>
      <body>
         <div subtype="1" type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="mc008a.small.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="place">Talladega</name>
                     <date when="1835-05-05">May 5th 1835</date>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <salute>Dear Brother</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>sir I want some Iron We are entirely out and it is Badly needed, <name type="person">Tucker</name> and myself are <choice>
                  <orig>puting</orig>
                  <reg>putting</reg>
               </choice> up a Blacksmith shop and we Want a <choice>
                  <orig>quanty</orig>
                  <reg>quantity</reg>
               </choice> of Iron, and all the Shops are out here I <choice>
                  <orig>Bot</orig>
                  <reg>Bought</reg>
               </choice>
               <del type="overstrike">Col.</del> Couls. Bacon  and has Sold out Bacon will do well.  Flour is <choice>
                  <orig>verry</orig>
                  <reg>very</reg>
               </choice> fast at Ten dollars, send Some Iron by the first <choice>
                  <orig>Waggon</orig>
                  <reg>Wagon</reg>
               </choice> that <choice>
                  <orig>halls</orig>
                  <reg>hauls</reg>
               </choice> for us I have sold Bacon at 12Â½ <choice>
                  <abbr>cts</abbr>
                  <expan>cents</expan>
               </choice>
            </p>
            <p>all is well.  Show this to <name type="person">Welcker</name>
               <name type="person">Carson</name> is in a powerful pet about his Iron for that horse Send all you Can for you Cant keep me Supplied</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>yours respectfully</salute>
               <signed>
                  <name type="person">Richard Grantham</name>
               </signed>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>To <name type="person">J. Grantham</name>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>&amp;</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="person">
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>C</abbr>
                           <expan>Charles</expan>
                        </choice> F. <emph>Welcker</emph>
                     </name>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
            </closer>
         </div>
